        private static string FeaturedPostsJson = @"{""status"":""ok"",""count"":8,""pages"":12,""tag"":{""id"":232,""slug"":""featured"",""title"":""featured"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":93},""posts"":[{""id"":7128,""type"":""post"",""slug"":""windows-phone-8s-og-windows-phone-8x-fra-htc"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/2012\/09\/19\/windows-phone-8s-og-windows-phone-8x-fra-htc\/"",""status"":""publish"",""title"":""Windows Phone 8S og Windows Phone 8X fra HTC"",""title_plain"":""Windows Phone 8S og Windows Phone 8X fra HTC"",""content"":""\r\n<!--Ad Injection mfunc mode ad include code--><!--mfunc include_once('\/var\/www\/windowsphonefan.dk\/public_html\/wp-content\/plugins\/ad-injection\/adshow.php') --><!--\/mfunc-->\r\n<p style=\""text-align: center;\""><a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X.jpeg\""><img class=\""aligncenter  wp-image-7130\"" title=\""HTC8S8X\"" src=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X.jpeg\"" alt=\""\"" width=\""512\"" height=\""338\"" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>HTC har netop l\u00f8ftet sl\u00f8ret for deres kommende Windows Phone modeller.<br \/>\nDer er tale om to nye telefoner nemlig, <strong>Windows Phone 8S<\/strong> og <strong>Windows Phone 8X<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>Mobil.nu har f\u00e5et en lille pr\u00e6sentation af 8X af den danske HTC direkt\u00f8r <a href=\""http:\/\/www.mobil.nu\/nyheder\/video-her-er-htc-windows-phone-8x-1.511951.html\"">som kan ses her<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>The Verge har ogs\u00e5 f\u00e5et lov at pille lidt ved disse nye telefoner, desv\u00e6rre har de heller ikke lov at se andet end startsk\u00e6rmen, ligesom vi s\u00e5 det ved Nokia&#8217;s event, s\u00e5 intet nyt om Windows Phone 8 endnu.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\""http:\/\/www.theverge.com\/2012\/9\/19\/3345684\/windows-phone-8x-by-htc-specs-release-date-features\"">L\u00e6s om HTC&#8217;s Windows Phone 8X her<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\""http:\/\/www.theverge.com\/2012\/9\/19\/3345712\/windows-phone-8s-by-htc-specs-release-date-features\"">L\u00e6s om HTC&#8217;s Windows Phone 8S her<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Man m\u00e5 sige at producenterne af Windows Phone telefoner virkelig har gjort noget ud af det denne gang, senest her med HTC som ser ud til at komme med nogle virkelig l\u00e6kre telefoner.<\/p>\n<p>Nu har jeg ikke f\u00e5et l\u00e6st om disse telefoner i detaljer men jeg har f\u00f8r kommenteret p\u00e5 at jeg synes at b\u00e5de Nokia og Samsung&#8217;s telefoner er ved at blive for store. Helt personligt vil jeg helst ikke have en telefon med en 4+ tommer sk\u00e6rm, synes simpelthen de bliver for store at have i h\u00e5nden.<br \/>\nDet er selvf\u00f8lgelig meget subjektivt, men s\u00e5dan har jeg det nu engang.<br \/>\nDet er derfor gl\u00e6deligt at se at HTC her kommer med en 4&#8243; telefon i form af 8S.<\/p>\n<p>Nu st\u00e5r man s\u00e5 bare med &#8220;problemet&#8221; &#8211; hvilket en skal man v\u00e6lge? :)<\/p>\n<p>Hvad synes I?<\/p>\n<p>Tak for tippet til <a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/forum\/viewtopic.php?f=6&amp;t=902\"">Briso<\/a>\u00a0og Jakob.<\/p>\n"",""excerpt"":""HTC har netop l\u00f8ftet sl\u00f8ret for deres kommende Windows Phone modeller. Der er tale om to nye telefoner nemlig, Windows Phone 8S og Windows Phone 8X. Mobil.nu har f\u00e5et en lille pr\u00e6sentation af 8X af den danske HTC direkt\u00f8r som kan ses her. The Verge har ogs\u00e5 f\u00e5et lov at pille lidt ved disse nye [...]"",""date"":""2012-09-19 21:20:17"",""modified"":""2012-09-19 21:25:32"",""categories"":[{""id"":12,""slug"":""windows-phone-nyheder"",""title"":""Windows Phone Nyheder"",""description"":""Seneste Windows Phone Nyheder"",""parent"":381,""post_count"":443}],""tags"":[{""id"":232,""slug"":""featured"",""title"":""featured"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":93},{""id"":234,""slug"":""full-image"",""title"":""full-image"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":80},{""id"":100,""slug"":""htc"",""title"":""htc"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":11},{""id"":471,""slug"":""windows-phone-8s"",""title"":""Windows Phone 8S"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":1},{""id"":472,""slug"":""windows-phone-8x"",""title"":""Windows Phone 8X"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":1}],""author"":{""id"":1,""slug"":""mads"",""name"":""Mads"",""first_name"":""Mads"",""last_name"":""Laumann"",""nickname"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk"",""description"":""""},""comments"":[{""id"":3798,""name"":""TLN"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-19 21:33:53"",""content"":""<p>ligesom dig kunne det v\u00e6re l\u00e6kkert med en 4&#8243; der dog har specs som en topmodel. Det synes jeg ikke vi f\u00e5r her. Det er lidt en WP7.5model bare med dualcore.<br \/>\nDualcore for mig er mindre interessant end LTE og NFC &#8211; med mindre WP8 ikke er helt s\u00e5 smooth som vi kender det fra WP7.5&#8230;<br \/>\nOg s\u00e5 er der sk\u00e6rmens opl\u00f8sning, hmm tja, tjo&#8230; S\u00e5 gerne den justeret!<br \/>\nSelve sk\u00e6rmen s\u00e5 ud til at v\u00e6re lige som HTCs andre WP modeller(en video p\u00e5 mobil.nu mener jeg det var) og de har alts\u00e5 f\u00e5et lidt kritik. Jeg har ikke selv haft en HTC WPmodel, men har oplevet dem ved siden af Lumia 800 da den blev lanceret og der var HTC noget bagud, s\u00e5 jeg h\u00e5ber HTC har oppet sig!<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0},{""id"":3799,""name"":""BallonPedro"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-20 11:08:25"",""content"":""<p>Hold da op, HTC har virkelig taget sig sammen. De plejer at spytte den ene billige (halvgrimme) model ud efter den anden, men dem her ser top nice ud ;-)<\/p>\n<p>Kan is\u00e6r godt lide de afrundede hj\u00f8rner, det for Lumia 920 til at se k\u00e6mpe ud i forhold til, hvilket den ikke er.<br \/>\nDen matte finish er ogs\u00e5 bestemt et plus. H\u00e5ber nemlig ikke alle 920 kommer i glossy.<br \/>\nV\u00e6gten pp 130g er ogs\u00e5 lige i skabet, igen i forhold til 920.<br \/>\nOg nu kan iPhone ikke l\u00e6ngere blande sig i ppi r\u00e6set, nu ligger Lumia og HTC p\u00e6nt foran ;-)<\/p>\n<p>En ting jeg dog altid har hadet ved HTC modeller, er deres Sense UI. Kan desv\u00e6rre se de pr\u00f8ver at f\u00f8re det med over i WP8 og s\u00e5 er det da pludselig ikke &#8220;den rene WP8 oplevelse&#8221; som en signaturmobil skulle v\u00e6re? Desuden ser det da noller ud med 2 ure p\u00e5 fronten, WP8&#8242;s eget i toppen og et k\u00e6mpe HTC sense lignende lige nedenunder ;-)<\/p>\n<p>Gl\u00e6der mig til at kunne pr\u00f8ve dem, lige nu ligger valget mellem 8X og 920.<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0}],""attachments"":[{""id"":7130,""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X.jpeg"",""slug"":""htc8s8x"",""title"":""HTC8S8X"",""description"":"""",""caption"":"""",""parent"":7128,""mime_type"":""image\/jpeg"",""images"":{""full"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X.jpeg"",""width"":640,""height"":423},""thumbnail"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-150x150.jpeg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""medium"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-300x198.jpeg"",""width"":300,""height"":198},""large"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X.jpeg"",""width"":640,""height"":423},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-3"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-150x150.jpeg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-4"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-100x100.jpeg"",""width"":100,""height"":100},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-5"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X.jpeg"",""width"":""640"",""height"":""423""},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-6"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-85x85.jpeg"",""width"":85,""height"":85},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-2"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-150x150.jpeg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-7"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-65x65.jpeg"",""width"":65,""height"":65}}}],""comment_count"":2,""comment_status"":""open"",""thumbnail"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/HTC8S8X-150x150.jpeg""},{""id"":7077,""type"":""post"",""slug"":""windows-phone-8-rtm"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/2012\/09\/15\/windows-phone-8-rtm\/"",""status"":""publish"",""title"":""Windows Phone 8 RTM"",""title_plain"":""Windows Phone 8 RTM"",""content"":""\r\n<!--Ad Injection mfunc mode ad include code--><!--mfunc include_once('\/var\/www\/windowsphonefan.dk\/public_html\/wp-content\/plugins\/ad-injection\/adshow.php') --><!--\/mfunc-->\r\n<p><a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm.jpg\""><img class=\""aligncenter size-full wp-image-7078\"" title=\""windows-phone-8-rtm\"" src=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm.jpg\"" alt=\""\"" width=\""600\"" height=\""373\"" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Windows Phone 8 skulle netop v\u00e6re blev &#8220;Released to\u00a0manufacturers&#8221; (RTM), hvilket betyder at selve Windows Phone 8 nu er f\u00e6rdigt. Alle producenterne s\u00e5 som Nokia, Samsung, HTC, LG osv. f\u00e5r nu denne version og kan s\u00e5 begynde at l\u00e6kke den p\u00e5 deres telefoner.<\/p>\n<p>Men f\u00f8r vi nu klapper vi vores sm\u00e5 n\u00f8rde h\u00e6nder, s\u00e5 skal vi nok ikke lige forvente at f\u00e5 en Windows Phone 8 telefon om en uge eller to :)<\/p>\n<p>Kan ikke huske hvor jeg l\u00e6ste det, men mener at Windows Phone 8 telefonerne skulle begynde at blive solgt fra slut oktober\/november og nok n\u00e6rmere i november end i oktober. S\u00e5 der er stadigv\u00e6k lige nogle uger vi skal vente &#8211; men Windows Phone 8 har aldrig v\u00e6ret s\u00e5 t\u00e6t p\u00e5 som nu.<\/p>\n<p>Udviklere kan fx allerede nu ans\u00f8ge om at f\u00e5 fingrene i en <a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/2012\/09\/14\/nu-kan-du-ansoge-om-windows-phone-8-sdk-preview\/\"">Preview version af Windows Phone 8 SDK&#8217;et<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Tak for tippet til Jan.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\""http:\/\/www.engadget.com\/2012\/09\/14\/windows-phone-8-rtm\/\"">Kilde<\/a><\/p>\n"",""excerpt"":""Windows Phone 8 skulle netop v\u00e6re blev &#8220;Released to\u00a0manufacturers&#8221; (RTM), hvilket betyder at selve Windows Phone 8 nu er f\u00e6rdigt. Alle producenterne s\u00e5 som Nokia, Samsung, HTC, LG osv. f\u00e5r nu denne version og kan s\u00e5 begynde at l\u00e6kke den p\u00e5 deres telefoner. Men f\u00f8r vi nu klapper vi vores sm\u00e5 n\u00f8rde h\u00e6nder, s\u00e5 skal [...]"",""date"":""2012-09-15 20:56:13"",""modified"":""2012-09-15 20:57:07"",""categories"":[{""id"":12,""slug"":""windows-phone-nyheder"",""title"":""Windows Phone Nyheder"",""description"":""Seneste Windows Phone Nyheder"",""parent"":381,""post_count"":443}],""tags"":[{""id"":232,""slug"":""featured"",""title"":""featured"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":93},{""id"":234,""slug"":""full-image"",""title"":""full-image"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":80},{""id"":132,""slug"":""rtm"",""title"":""rtm"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":3},{""id"":327,""slug"":""windows-phone-8"",""title"":""windows phone 8"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":36}],""author"":{""id"":1,""slug"":""mads"",""name"":""Mads"",""first_name"":""Mads"",""last_name"":""Laumann"",""nickname"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk"",""description"":""""},""comments"":[{""id"":3757,""name"":""BallonPedro"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-16 19:54:23"",""content"":""<p>Jeg klapper alligevel lidt for mig selv ;-)<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0},{""id"":3760,""name"":""Alexander Mortensen"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-17 10:34:28"",""content"":""<p>S\u00e5 h\u00e5ber jeg bare lidt at der kommer noget gang i Windows Store, s\u00e5 man kan f\u00e5 nogle dejlige apps til min kommende Lumia 920 :)<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0},{""id"":3764,""name"":""Henrik"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-17 19:20:07"",""content"":""<p>Jeg m\u00e5 indr\u00f8mme, det irriterer mig at m\u00e5ske skulle vente op til 2,5 m\u00e5ned endnu&#8230;og mon ikke der reelt kan g\u00e5 endnu l\u00e6ngere tid, synes det er br\u00e6nd \u00e6rgerligt, men mest fordi Microsoft ik har meldt noget som helst ud om hvad man f\u00e5r af nye features, kommer man til at kunne v\u00e6lge egne mp3 sange som ringetoner eller SMS toner? Hvor \u00e5bent bliver systemet? N\u00e5r man Eks s\u00e6tter den til ens Windows pc kan man s\u00e5 tr\u00e6kke\/slippe indhold til og fra pc til mobil og den anden vej liges\u00e5? I min verden lover det ikke specielt godt de ikke har meldt noget ud endnu, og frygter systemet bliver blodfattigt p\u00e5 muligheder og nyheder i forhold til det gamle system.<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0},{""id"":3766,""name"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk"",""date"":""2012-09-17 20:25:04"",""content"":""<p>@Henrik: M\u00e5ske f\u00e5r du ret, m\u00e5ske ikke.<br \/>\nDet som Microsoft har sagt er at de vil vente med at pr\u00e6sentere mange af de her nye features til vi kommer t\u00e6ttere p\u00e5 den reelle Windows Phone 8 lancering.<br \/>\nAntager at det er for at folk ikke skal n\u00e5 at glemme hvad Windows Phone 8 kan, inden telefonerne kommer i butikkerne.<\/p>\n<p>S\u00e5 jeg v\u00e6lger at v\u00e6re optimist til det sidste og vil sige at bare de ting vi allerede har f\u00e5et at vide da er k\u00e6mpe store ting. Fx muligheden for native kode og Unity3D support. Det g\u00f8r at vi nok vil se alle de gode iPhone spil p\u00e5 Windows Phone. Derudover giver native kode support ogs\u00e5 en masse muligheder for apps som der ikke har v\u00e6ret f\u00f8r.<\/p>\n<p>Vi m\u00e5 se, sp\u00e6ndende efter\u00e5r i hvert fald :)<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0,""author"":{""id"":1,""slug"":""mads"",""name"":""Mads"",""first_name"":""Mads"",""last_name"":""Laumann"",""nickname"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk"",""description"":""""}},{""id"":3777,""name"":""BallonPedro"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-18 08:15:17"",""content"":""<p>Ja, ventetiden er tr\u00e6ls :-\/<\/p>\n<p>Og det er super \u00e6rgeligt at MS ikke er f\u00e6rdig med WP8 endnu, is\u00e6r n\u00e5r der er pr\u00e6senteret nye mobiler med det kommende system.<\/p>\n<p>Det var super at f.eks. Nokia n\u00e5ede at pr\u00e6sentere deres mobiler lige inden Apple, det giver noget medieomtale og fastholder folk i at vente p\u00e5 f.eks. Lumia 920.<\/p>\n<p>Men der hvor Apple virkelig vinder, det er at pr\u00e6sentere en mobil og s\u00e5 kunne levere den knap 2 uger efter. DET er der ingen andre der form\u00e5r.<\/p>\n<p>Der skulle Nokia og MS have gjort det samme og v\u00e6ret helt klar med mobiler til salg nu her. S\u00e5 havde der v\u00e6ret mere konkurrence og Nokia ville f\u00e5 boostet deres salg.<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0}],""attachments"":[{""id"":7078,""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm.jpg"",""slug"":""windows-phone-8-rtm"",""title"":""windows-phone-8-rtm"",""description"":"""",""caption"":"""",""parent"":7077,""mime_type"":""image\/jpeg"",""images"":{""full"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm.jpg"",""width"":600,""height"":373},""thumbnail"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-150x150.jpg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""medium"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-300x186.jpg"",""width"":300,""height"":186},""large"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm.jpg"",""width"":600,""height"":373},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-3"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-150x150.jpg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-4"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-100x100.jpg"",""width"":100,""height"":100},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-5"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm.jpg"",""width"":""600"",""height"":""373""},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-6"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-85x85.jpg"",""width"":85,""height"":85},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-2"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-150x150.jpg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-7"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-65x65.jpg"",""width"":65,""height"":65}}}],""comment_count"":5,""comment_status"":""open"",""thumbnail"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/windows-phone-8-rtm-150x150.jpg""},{""id"":6949,""type"":""post"",""slug"":""paa-aftentur-med-nokia-lumia-920-uden-snyd"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/2012\/09\/10\/paa-aftentur-med-nokia-lumia-920-uden-snyd\/"",""status"":""publish"",""title"":""P\u00e5 aftentur med Nokia Lumia 920 &#8211; se hvad den kan uden snyd"",""title_plain"":""P\u00e5 aftentur med Nokia Lumia 920 &#8211; se hvad den kan uden snyd"",""content"":""\r\n<!--Ad Injection mfunc mode ad include code--><!--mfunc include_once('\/var\/www\/windowsphonefan.dk\/public_html\/wp-content\/plugins\/ad-injection\/adshow.php') --><!--\/mfunc-->\r\n<p style=\""text-align: center;\""><a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge.jpg\""><img class=\""aligncenter  wp-image-6950\"" title=\""nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge\"" src=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge.jpg\"" alt=\""\"" width=\""612\"" height=\""344\"" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Da Nokia i sidste uge\u00a0annoncerede Nokia Lumia 820 og Nokia Lumia 920 var jeg personlig mest imponeret over de film og foto eksemplar vi f\u00e5 fra Lumia 920. Her var endelig noget som s\u00e5 ud til at flytte baren en smule, ja n\u00e6rmest for godt til at v\u00e6re sandt.<\/p>\n<p>Nogle timer gik og det vidste sig at det rent faktisk\u00a0<em>var<\/em> <a href=\""http:\/\/beep.tv2.dk\/nyheder\/nokia-undskylder-se-hvordan-de-sn%C3%B8d\"">for godt til at v\u00e6re sandt<\/a>. K\u00e6mpe selvm\u00e5l af Nokia p\u00e5 et meget kritisk tidspunkt &#8211; desv\u00e6rre :(<\/p>\n<p>Nu pr\u00f8ver Nokia s\u00e5 at g\u00f8re sagen god igen. De har nemlig inviteret <a href=\""http:\/\/www.theverge.com\/2012\/9\/7\/3299784\/nokia-lumia-920-pureview-camera-hi-res-photos\"">The Verge<\/a>\u00a0ud og pr\u00f8ve Nokia Lumia 920 s\u00e5 de med egne \u00f8je kan se at det er en fantastisk kamera mobil.<\/p>\n<p><script src=\""http:\/\/player.ooyala.com\/player.js?width=625&#038;height=450&#038;embedCode=1yMHJ0NToApMi7AYNVD5SlphieZxE7nN&#038;deepLinkEmbedCode=1yMHJ0NToApMi7AYNVD5SlphieZxE7nN&#038;video_pcode=ppbnY65tdYh_HxFfIkVstq2Iq_oQ\""><\/script><\/p>\n<p>Se flere billeder og l\u00e6s om tured p\u00e5 <a href=\""http:\/\/www.theverge.com\/2012\/9\/7\/3299784\/nokia-lumia-920-pureview-camera-hi-res-photos\"">The Verge&#8217;s side<\/a>.<\/p>\n"",""excerpt"":""Da Nokia i sidste uge\u00a0annoncerede Nokia Lumia 820 og Nokia Lumia 920 var jeg personlig mest imponeret over de film og foto eksemplar vi f\u00e5 fra Lumia 920. Her var endelig noget som s\u00e5 ud til at flytte baren en smule, ja n\u00e6rmest for godt til at v\u00e6re sandt. Nogle timer gik og det vidste [...]"",""date"":""2012-09-10 22:56:23"",""modified"":""2012-09-10 22:56:47"",""categories"":[{""id"":12,""slug"":""windows-phone-nyheder"",""title"":""Windows Phone Nyheder"",""description"":""Seneste Windows Phone Nyheder"",""parent"":381,""post_count"":443}],""tags"":[{""id"":232,""slug"":""featured"",""title"":""featured"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":93},{""id"":234,""slug"":""full-image"",""title"":""full-image"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":80},{""id"":413,""slug"":""nokia-lumia-920"",""title"":""nokia lumia 920"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":10},{""id"":327,""slug"":""windows-phone-8"",""title"":""windows phone 8"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":36}],""author"":{""id"":1,""slug"":""mads"",""name"":""Mads"",""first_name"":""Mads"",""last_name"":""Laumann"",""nickname"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk"",""description"":""""},""comments"":[{""id"":3715,""name"":""BallonPedro"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-11 06:33:59"",""content"":""<p>Ja, m\u00e5 sige at kameraet imponerer og mega \u00f8v med den reklamebummert ;-)<\/p>\n<p>Gl\u00e6der mig dog til selv at pr\u00f8ve det og se hvordan det er i forhold til p\u00e5 800&#8242;ern.<\/p>\n<p>800 har nemlig en rigtig d\u00e5rlig autofokus. N\u00e5r man skal tage et billede begynder det f\u00f8rst at fokusere efter man trykker knappen halvt ind. Og i videodelen skal autofokus sl\u00e5es fra og til igen hver gang man skal filme, ellers er det bare en helt sl\u00f8ret video man f\u00e5r.<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0}],""attachments"":[{""id"":6950,""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge.jpg"",""slug"":""nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge"",""title"":""nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge"",""description"":"""",""caption"":"""",""parent"":6949,""mime_type"":""image\/jpeg"",""images"":{""full"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge.jpg"",""width"":1020,""height"":574},""thumbnail"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-150x150.jpg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""medium"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-300x168.jpg"",""width"":300,""height"":168},""large"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge.jpg"",""width"":1020,""height"":574},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-3"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-150x150.jpg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-4"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-100x100.jpg"",""width"":100,""height"":100},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-5"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge.jpg"",""width"":""1020"",""height"":""574""},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-6"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-85x85.jpg"",""width"":85,""height"":85},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-2"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-150x150.jpg"",""width"":150,""height"":150},""cat_post_thumb_sizecategoryposts-7"":{""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-65x65.jpg"",""width"":65,""height"":65}}}],""comment_count"":1,""comment_status"":""open"",""thumbnail"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2012\/09\/nokia-lumia-920-sample-the-verge-150x150.jpg""},{""id"":6914,""type"":""post"",""slug"":""windowsphonefan-dk-skifter-navn-til-windowsfan-dk"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\/2012\/09\/09\/windowsphonefan-dk-skifter-navn-til-windowsfan-dk\/"",""status"":""publish"",""title"":""WindowsPhoneFan.dk skifter navn til WindowsFan.dk"",""title_plain"":""WindowsPhoneFan.dk skifter navn til WindowsFan.dk"",""content"":""\r\n<!--Ad Injection mfunc mode ad include code--><!--mfunc include_once('\/var\/www\/windowsphonefan.dk\/public_html\/wp-content\/plugins\/ad-injection\/adshow.php') --><!--\/mfunc-->\r\n<p>I forl\u00e6ngelse af den nye <a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsphonefan.dk\/2012\/07\/09\/windowsphonefan-dk-har-faet-ny-startskaerm\/\"">forside her p\u00e5 WindowsPhoneFan.dk<\/a>,\u00a0som introducerede Windows 8 nyheder, kommer nu et navneskift.<br \/>\nDet ser ud til at Windows Phone (8) og Windows (8) i fremtiden vil smelte mere og mere sammen. B\u00e5de i form af at de ligner hinanden og reelt k\u00f8rer p\u00e5 samme kerne, men ogs\u00e5 at de integrerer med hinanden.<br \/>\nFor at underbygge dette kommer <strong>WindowsPhoneFan.dk<\/strong> til at skifte navn til <strong>WindowsFan.dk<\/strong> her i l\u00f8bet af den kommende uge (det er planen i hvert fald).<\/p>\n<p>Forh\u00e5bentlig bliver det problemfrit for jer brugere og i vil intet opleve andet end nyt dom\u00e6ne og navn :)<\/p>\n<p>Jeg skal nok skrive indl\u00e6g hvis der er nogle v\u00e6sentlige \u00e6ndringer som I skal v\u00e6re opm\u00e6rksomme p\u00e5, fx ny twitter konto, ny youtube konto osv. Jeg har ikke endelig besluttet om jeg kommer til at \u00e6ndre dem endnu, men hvis jeg g\u00f8r skal jeg selvf\u00f8lgelig nok g\u00f8re opm\u00e6rksom p\u00e5 det.<\/p>\n<p>Skulle i dog opleve problemer p\u00e5 siden, noget der ikke fungerer som det plejer eller andet, s\u00e5 m\u00e5 i endelig sige til!<br \/>\nBare skriv til mig via <a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsphonefan.dk\/kontakt\/\"">kontakt formularen<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Udover at navnet skifter vil der ikke umiddelbart v\u00e6re andre \u00e6ndringer.\u00a0Dvs. alt indholdet er som det plejer, din bruger til forummet er som den plejer osv. I virkeligheden er det det samme site, bare under andet dom\u00e6ne.<\/p>\n<p>Du skal ikke engang huske nyt dom\u00e6ne hvis du ikke gider, b\u00e5de <a href=\""http:\/\/www.wpfan.dk\"">wpfan.dk<\/a> og <a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsphonefan.dk\"">windowsphonefan.dk<\/a> vil ryge over p\u00e5 <a href=\""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk\"">windowsfan.dk<\/a> &#8211; s\u00e5 ingen grund til bekymring :)<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e5ber I kan lide det nye navn og vil tage godt imod det.<\/p>\n<p>God s\u00f8ndag.<\/p>\n"",""excerpt"":""I forl\u00e6ngelse af den nye forside her p\u00e5 WindowsPhoneFan.dk,\u00a0som introducerede Windows 8 nyheder, kommer nu et navneskift. Det ser ud til at Windows Phone (8) og Windows (8) i fremtiden vil smelte mere og mere sammen. B\u00e5de i form af at de ligner hinanden og reelt k\u00f8rer p\u00e5 samme kerne, men ogs\u00e5 at de integrerer [...]"",""date"":""2012-09-09 20:21:32"",""modified"":""2012-09-09 20:21:32"",""categories"":[{""id"":3,""slug"":""andre-nyheder-nyheder"",""title"":""Andre nyheder"",""description"":"""",""parent"":381,""post_count"":67}],""tags"":[{""id"":232,""slug"":""featured"",""title"":""featured"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":93},{""id"":234,""slug"":""full-image"",""title"":""full-image"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":80},{""id"":53,""slug"":""windowsphonefan-dk"",""title"":""windowsphonefan.dk"",""description"":"""",""post_count"":8}],""author"":{""id"":1,""slug"":""mads"",""name"":""Mads"",""first_name"":""Mads"",""last_name"":""Laumann"",""nickname"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk"",""description"":""""},""comments"":[{""id"":3713,""name"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsphonefan.dk"",""date"":""2012-09-10 22:17:51"",""content"":""<p>Tester lige om kommentarer stadigv\u00e6k virker efter skiftet til nyt dom\u00e6ne :)<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0,""author"":{""id"":1,""slug"":""mads"",""name"":""Mads"",""first_name"":""Mads"",""last_name"":""Laumann"",""nickname"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsfan.dk"",""description"":""""}},{""id"":3714,""name"":""sarasera"",""url"":"""",""date"":""2012-09-11 06:15:32"",""content"":""<p>Hvor er forum?<\/p>\n"",""parent"":0},{""id"":3716,""name"":""Mads"",""url"":""http:\/\/www.windowsphonefan.dk"",""date"":""2012-09-11 10:40:09"",""content"":""<p>@sarasera: Linket oppe i toppen i menuen skulle ger stad